snippet.title: Quake: Halloween Jam 2 - Misadventure Galley
snippet.description:
Playthrough of "Misadventure Galley" (hwjam2_greenwood.bsp), a custom Q1 single player map made by Greenwood for the Halloween Jam 2 map-pack. 

Start map "House of Horrors" made by NewHouse.

Release Date: 31/10/2019
Download (hwjam2.zip): 
https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/hwjam2.html

Skill 2 Hard
Secrets = 3/7
Kills = 100/100

Game: Quake
http://store.steampowered.com/app/2310/QUAKE/
Custom Engine: Quakespasm-Spiked 
http://triptohell.info/moodles/qss/

Soundtrack: "Alternate Quake Music" pack updated
https://www.quaketastic.com/files/music/aqm2_pack.zip
